Pre-Game Insights: The Chicago White Sox head into the matchup with the Baltimore Orioles after losing 11 in a row.
Baltimore has an 80-59 record overall and a 40-30 record in home games.
Chicago has a 31-108 record overall and a 13-54 record on the road.
Tuesday's game is the sixth time these teams square off this season. The Orioles have a 5-0 advantage in the season series.
